Kaneda!

384
00:36:47,622 --> 00:36:51,583
So, what's the matter?
Try telling me about it.

385
00:36:51,792 --> 00:36:54,419
I had a dream.

386
00:36:54,629 --> 00:36:56,254
A dream?

387
00:36:57,798 --> 00:37:02,761
