390
00:37:09,936 --> 00:37:11,102
Akira?!

391
00:37:11,312 --> 00:37:18,276
The city will crumble,
and so many people will die...

392
00:37:18,486 --> 00:37:22,197
When?! When will it happen, Kiyoko?!

